subSections.title: Readings
Compounds
subSections.text:
{{der-top|Compounds}}
* {{ja-r|無%明|む%みょう}}: [[unenlightment]]; [[ignorance]] of [[nirvana]]
* {{ja-r|神%無%月|かん%な%づき}}: {{qualifier|archaic}} the tenth month of the lunar calendar
* {{ja-r|無%形|む%ぎょう}}: [[formlessness]], [[bodylessness]]; something [[shapeless]] and [[invisible]]
* {{ja-r|無%形|む%けい}}: [[intangibility]]; [[incorporeality]]
* {{ja-r|無%見|む%けん}}: the belief that everything in this world is completely [[null]] and [[void]], with no [[substance]]
* {{ja-r|無%名|む%めい}}: [[nameless]], [[anonymous]], [[unsigned]]; [[anonymity]]
* {{ja-r|無%用|む%よう}}: [[futility]]; [[uselessness]]
* {{ja-r|無%機|む%き}}: [[inorganic]]
{{der-mid}}
* {{ja-r|無%双|む%そう}}: [[matchless]], [[peerless]]
* {{ja-r|苦%無|く%ない}}: a [[kunai#Japanese|kunai]]
* {{ja-r|無%月|む%げつ}}: when the [[moon]] is not [[visible]] due to [[rain]] or some other reason
* {{ja-r|無%精|ぶ%しょう}}: [[laziness]]
* {{ja-r|無%力|む%りょく}}: [[powerless]]; [[incompetent]]
* {{ja-r|無%力%感|む%りょく%かん}}: a [[feeling]] of [[powerlessness]]
* {{ja-r|無%意%識|む%い%しき}}: [[unconscious]], [[unconsciousness]]
* {{ja-r|無%限|む%げん}}: [[infinity]]; [[limitless]]; [[unlimited]]
* {{ja-r|無%人|ぶ%にん}}: [[uninhabited]], [[unmanned]]
{{der-bottom}}

{{ja-kanjitab|yomi=o|む}}
